 <title>Making Cow Dung Based Soap</title>
 <link>http://www.careforcows.org/news/making_cow_dung_based_soap</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;150&quot; height=&quot;133&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;/images/store/soap.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Care for Cows soap is made with cow dung, multani mitthi (a clay like Fuller&amp;rsquo;s Earth), gehru powder (red clay), sesame oil, Neem extract, and camphor. This combination offers an organic, gentle cleansing, moisturizing, antiseptic soap.&lt;/p&gt;
